{"tid":629840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★僱主請cheap人不是夢 政府考慮為聘用60歲以上的僱主發放4000元津貼","createTime":"2018-04-15T05:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T04:56:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"333de5086a2d8aff8a01c38caa24d53cda69674b","tid":629840,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"港府去年施政報告中提出設立人力資源規劃委員會，於本月9日召開首次會議，主持會議的政務司司長張建宗今日（15日）撰寫網誌，講述港府正推行的人力資源政策，包括考慮延長公務員工作年期、為聘用60歲以上退休人士的僱主發放4000元津貼等，冀能提升社會勞動力的質與量，而過去10年的年長勞動人口參與率有所上升，由2007年的5.2%，升至2017年的11%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/178299/張建宗指年長勞動人口參與率過去10年有上升-將全面釋放勞動力\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F178299%2F%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E6%8C%87%E5%B9%B4%E9%95%B7%E5%8B%9E%E5%8B%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%8E%87%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB10%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E5%B0%87%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%8B%9E%E5%8B%95%E5%8A%9B&d=wjLnzjBMS3ebGeoGKzojcMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=eab444c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/178299/張建宗指年長勞動人口參與率過去10年有上升-將全面釋放勞動力</a>"},{"pid":"58ee870199cff7bb821be7280e45608d09fcfc37","tid":629840,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T05:03:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/178299/張建宗指年長勞動人口參與率過去10年有上升-將全面釋放勞動力\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F178299%2F%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97%E6%8C%87%E5%B9%B4%E9%95%B7%E5%8B%9E%E5%8B%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%8E%87%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB10%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%89%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E5%B0%87%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%8B%9E%E5%8B%95%E5%8A%9B&d=wjLnzjBMS3ebGeoGKzojcMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=eab444c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/178299/張建宗指年長勞動人口參與率過去10年有上升-將全面釋放勞動力</a>"},{"pid":"32638975b4f3c849551f2020be1fe13136caa8c5","tid":6298